            </ui>
            <value>
               <text xliff:rid="14DC5172-4EE6-4DE4-A0F2-B5693110EF48">TERMS AND CONDITIONS : 1) Our responsibility ceases on delivery of goods to Transporter / as per individual P.O. 2)No Claim will be entertained  if not lodged within two weeks from the date of our invoice . 3) All   transactions and bills are subject to Pune Jurisdication. 4) Interest  @ 24% will be charged extra if not paid within agreed period.</text>
            </value>
